Title: 100 Gb/s complete ETDM system based on monolithically integrated transmitter and receiver modules
HostPublication: 2010 Conference on Optical Fiber Communication, Collocated National Fiber Optic Engineers Conference, OFC/NFOEC 2010
Keywords: BER performance;Monolithically integrated;System-based;Electric converters;Engineers;Monolithic integrated circuits;Optical communication;Optical fibers;Transmitters;Fibers
Abstract: A complete ETDM system based on monolithically integrated transmitter and receiver modules was demonstrated with BER performance below FEC threshold up to 107 Gb/s. ETDM signal at 112 Gb/s with clear eye opening was also observed.
